{
  "title": "Rarely Light Shaggy German Pork Grill",
  "description": "A sweet and light German dish featuring pork and tomato ketchup, perfect for a binchotan-grill. The Mediterranean-friendly flavors of this dish make it a great choice for a summer evening.",
