  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the binchotan grill to 180°C. ",
    "Mix the onion, garlic, fenugreek leaves, salt, and black pepper in a bowl.",
    "Place the pork shoulder on the grill and cook for 10 minutes on each side.",
    "Brush the pork with the honey and tomato ketchup mixture after 20 minutes of cooking.",
    "Deglaze the grill with the tomato ketchup and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Let the pork rest for 5 minutes before slicing and serving.",
    "Slice the pork into thin strips and serve hot.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve with your favorite sides."
